Class RangeSetBuilder<C extends Comparable>

  • java.lang.Object

  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    IndexRangeSetBuilder, PrunedPartitionBuilder

    public class RangeSetBuilder<C extends Comparable>
extends DefaultVisitor<com.google.common.collect.RangeSet<C>,Void>
    A builder can build a range set of type C. It also extends DefaultVisitor and override and LogicalBinaryExpression's visit. For ComparisonBinaryExpression, we cannot just override it because IndexRangeSetBuilder and LogicalBinaryExpression has different behavior. A method visitComparisonBinaryExpr is added with extra boolean variable to control the behavior.
